DOC.brief_summary: The study is a Proof-of-concept study to evaluate if DF01 can prevent protracted labor. Time to delivery will be measured from the time of at least 3 cm cervix dilatation and 3 contractions of minimum one minute's duration/10 minutes.
DOC.brief_title: Study to Assess Safety and Efficacy of DF01 in Reducing Prolonged Labor
DOC.criteria: healthy nulliparous females normal singleton pregnancy intact membranes breech or other abnormal presentation intercurrent illness pregnancy complications vaginal bleeding in third trimester etc
